Text.val: Application status must be smaller than 100 (3957)
Financial product type does not match with request (7086)
Fields that have to be checked either buildup or return
Yield percentage or Interest scale must be filled
Scale and duration does not exist in savings forms
Buildup, termDeposit and optional in default --> Deposit account
Return and optional --> Account for payment
